{"id":21091,"date":"2015-10-25T14:28:58","date_gmt":"2015-10-25T10:28:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=21091"},"modified":"2023-08-28T18:04:15","modified_gmt":"2023-08-28T14:04:15","slug":"prophet-condemns-killing-children","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/25\/prophet-condemns-killing-children\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Children: The Prophet condemns killing of children"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Aswad ibn Sari\u2019 reported: I came with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and participated in the battle with him. I engaged in the skirmish that day, until some people killed children. The Prophet was told about it and he said, \u201c<strong>What is wrong with these people transgressing the limits of killing, even having killed children?<\/strong>\u201d A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, they are only the children of idolaters.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>No doubt, the best of you are the children of idolaters<\/strong>.\u201d Then, the Prophet said, \u201c<strong>No doubt, do not kill children! Do not kill children! Every soul is born upon its natural instinct until he expresses it with his tongue, then his father turns him into a Jew or a Christian<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 15589<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0639\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u06